New Corporate Public Affairs Directory 2002-Available in December 2001

Columbia Books is pleased to announce that the 2002 edition of the National Directory of Corporate Public Affairs will be available in a few short weeks. This new edition is fully updated with over 1700 companies and contains contact information (including address, phone and fax numbers, and email addresses) for over 15,000 corporate public affairs executives.  This directory is a must-have for those interested in networking, fact-finding and coalition building within the public affairs community.

To order, go to www.columbiabooks.com or call 1-888-265-0600.


National Directory of Corporate Public Affairs 2002
Provides contact information for 15,000 corporate public affairs executives, as well as information on corporate giving programs, foundations, investor relations and PACs.

